(14013, 'Halayhi salaamaa man bihi qad mahaa laghwii', 7881, 1),
(14014, 'que les deux Prières de CELUI Qui a effacé ma vanité grâce à Lui soient sur Lui.', 7881, 2),
(14015, 'That both Prayers of the ONE Who erased my vanity, thanks to Him, be upon Him.', 7881, 3),
(14016, 'Waqaanii bihis suu-ii wa lii kaana bil munaa', 7882, 1),
